cility has successfully completed its first Health Canada inspection since being acquired by the company.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe two-week inspection confirmed Bora\\u2019s cGMP systems are in compliance with Health Canada standards.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Mississauga, Ontario site is one of Bora\\u2019s three state-of-the-art contract manufacturing (CMO) facilities worldwide which collectively supply pharmaceutical products to over 100 markets.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u201cThe successful completion of the Health Canada audit demonstrates that Bora Pharmaceuticals is dedicated to meeting the most stringent regulatory standards in the industry, and delivering the highest quality products to our clients,\\u201d said Bobby Sheng, CEO, Bora Pharmaceuticals.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Mississauga, Ontario site has also completed CGMP inspections by the U.S. FDA, the Japanese PMDA, ANVISA, Korean FDA, Turkish Ministry of Health, and the Russian Federation.\\r\\n\\r\\nAndrew Ehrat, General Manager at the site, added: \\u201cThe favorable outcome from this inspection reflects Bora\\u2019s commitment to continuous improvement in our quality systems and processes to meet the needs of our global clients.\\u201d\\r\\n\\r\\nBora acquired the Mississauga plant from GSK in late 2020. The site is the company\\u2019s first manufacturing facility in North America and is home to its headquarters in the region.\\r\\n\\r\\nAbout Bora Pharmaceuticals:\\r\\nBora Pharmaceuticals is a premier international CGMP CDMO specializing in complex oral solid dosage, non-sterile liquids, Nasal sprays, and semi-solids pharmaceutical Rx and OTC products for late-phase Clinical through Commercial manufacturing and packaging. Bora owns and operates three state-of-the-art CGMP manufacturing facilities (Taiwan and Canada) built to the highest international standards for manufacturing, packaging, R&D, and analytical testing. Our TAA-compliant sites deliver to more than 100 markets around the world including the USA, Canada, EU, Southeast Asia, Middle East, and South and Central Americas. Bora handles high potency compounds, solvents, flammables, and IR\\/SR\\/ER release profile products.\\r\\n\\r\\nFor further information please visit www.boracorpcdmo.com \\r\\n\\r\\nContact:\\r\\nFor Media enquires:\\r\\nLara Lovenbury\\r\\nPR Manager, Ramarketing\\r\\nlara@ramarketingpr.com \\r\\n+44(0)7732 681275\\r\\n\\r\\nLonnie Barish\\r\\nVice President, Business Development and Marketing\\r\\n1866-6PHARMA\\r\\nLonnie.barish@bora-corp.com\",\"zh_title\":\"\\u5bf6\\u4f86\\u88fd\\u85e5\\u5b8c\\u6210\\u52a0\\u62ff\\u5927\\u885b\\u751f\\u90e8\\u6aa2\\u67e5\",\"zh_details\":\"Bora Pharmaceuticals \\u7684\\u4e00\\u500b\\u90e8\\u9580 Bora Pharmaceutical Services Inc. \\u5ba3\\u5e03\\uff0c\\u5176\\u4f4d\\u65bc\\u5b89\\u5927\\u7565\\u7701\\u5bc6\\u897f\\u6c99\\u52a0\\u7684\\u5408\\u540c\\u88fd\\u9020\\u548c\\u5305\\u88dd\\u5de5\\u5ee0\\u5df2\\u6210\\u529f\\u5b8c\\u6210\\u81ea\\u88ab\\u8a72\\u516c\\u53f8\\u6536\\u8cfc\\u4ee5\\u4f86\\u7684\\u9996\\u6b21\\u52a0\\u62ff\\u5927\\u885b\\u751f\\u90e8\\u6aa2\\u67e5\\u3002\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u70ba\\u671f\\u5169\\u9031\\u7684\\u6aa2\\u67e5\\u78ba\\u8a8d Bora \\u7684 cGMP \\u7cfb\\u7d71\\u7b26\\u5408\\u52a0\\u62ff\\u5927\\u885b\\u751f\\u90e8\\u7684\\u6a19\\u6e96\\u3002\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u5b89\\u5927\\u7565\\u7701\\u5bc6\\u897f\\u6c99\\u52a0\\u5de5\\u5ee0\\u662f Bora \\u5168\\u7403\\u4e09\\u500b\\u6700\\u5148\\u9032\\u7684\\u5408\\u540c\\u88fd\\u9020 (CMO) \\u5de5\\u5ee0\\u4e4b\\u4e00\\uff0c\\u5171\\u540c\\u5411 100 \\u591a\\u500b\\u5e02\\u5834\\u4f9b\\u61c9\\u85e5\\u54c1\\u3002\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u201c\\u52a0\\u62ff\\u5927\\u885b\\u751f\\u90e8\\u5be9\\u6838\\u7684\\u6210\\u529f\\u5b8c\\u6210\\u8868\\u660e\\uff0cBora Pharmaceuticals \\u81f4\\u529b\\u65bc\\u6eff\\u8db3\\u884c\\u696d\\u6700\\u56b4\\u683c\\u7684\\u76e3\\u7ba1\\u6a19\\u6e96\\uff0c\\u4e26\\u70ba\\u6211\\u5011\\u7684\\u5ba2\\u6236\\u63d0\\u4f9b\\u6700\\u512a\\u8cea\\u7684\\u7522\\u54c1\\uff0c\\u201dBora Pharmaceuticals \\u9996\\u5e2d\\u57f7\\u